Broccoli, Cheese & Rice Casserole

1 cup uncooked instant rice			2(10 oz) packages frozen, chopped broccoli, 	
½ chopped onion				thawed & drained
¼ cup fat free milk				1(10oz) can cream of mushroom soup, 
4 oz light cheese, cubed			undiluted
2 tbs butter/ margarine, softened		


Directions
1. Preheat oven to 350 degrees 
2. 2. Combine all ingredients in a large bowl, and spoon into a 2 quart casserole
3. Bake at 350 degrees for 45 minutes
